1
00:00:17,208 --> 00:00:20,041
[Maka]
A sound soul...

2
00:00:20,125 --> 00:00:22,333
...dwells within a sound mind...

3
00:00:22,416 --> 00:00:25,083
...and a sound body.

4
00:00:30,291 --> 00:00:32,375
It's okay, really...

5
00:00:33,708 --> 00:00:35,666
I promise you.

6
00:00:40,208 --> 00:00:44,500
It's not that you don't know
how to deal with people...

7
00:00:44,583 --> 00:00:49,000
It's that no one ever took
the time to deal with you.

8
00:00:50,375 --> 00:00:52,333
What do you say?

9
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:56,791
Will you let me
be your friend, Crona...

10
00:00:56,875 --> 00:00:58,541
Please say you will.

11
00:01:15,625 --> 00:01:18,875
[Soul] You can't succeed without
the madness, huh...? Hah!

12
00:01:18,958 --> 00:01:21,250
How does it feel to
have been so wrong...?

13
00:01:21,333 --> 00:01:23,250
Maybe you should take
up a different hobby...

14
00:01:23,333 --> 00:01:26,000
The music thing
doesn't really suit you.

15
00:01:26,083 --> 00:01:29,833
[door groans and
shuts with echo]

16
00:01:29,916 --> 00:01:33,083
[Demon]
Oh... He left.

17
00:01:33,166 --> 00:01:34,791
Oh well, that's all right...

18
00:01:34,875 --> 00:01:37,916
The door will
always be unlocked.

19
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,041
But still...

20
00:01:39,125 --> 00:01:41,541
...what his girlie
did back there...

21
00:01:47,166 --> 00:01:49,833
Was it really an
exorcism wavelength?

22
00:01:50,583 --> 00:01:55,541
♪ opening song ♪

23
00:03:25,666 --> 00:03:28,000
The black blood has
been stopped somehow.

24
00:03:28,083 --> 00:03:30,000
The fight between Maka
and the Demon Sword at the

25
00:03:30,083 --> 00:03:31,791
second barrier has ended...

26
00:03:31,875 --> 00:03:35,125
I can feel both of their
souls beginning to relax now.

27
00:03:35,208 --> 00:03:37,458
And Maka...?

28
00:03:37,541 --> 00:03:39,291
Is my darling daughter alright?

29
00:03:39,375 --> 00:03:40,541
She is...

30
00:03:40,625 --> 00:03:42,125
It looks like she was
able to grasp on to the

31
00:03:42,208 --> 00:03:44,875
Demon Sword's
wavelength somehow...

32
00:03:44,958 --> 00:03:48,625
The sword meister's
wavelength is stabilizing.

33
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:53,416
[Crona] I've never cried this
much before in my life.

34
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:55,500
How am I supposed
to deal with my tears...?

35
00:03:55,583 --> 00:03:58,833
There're so many of them.

36
00:03:58,916 --> 00:04:01,958
[Soul] Maka, we're
running out of time.

37
00:04:03,041 --> 00:04:04,583
We need to get moving.

38
00:04:04,666 --> 00:04:06,250
But we can't just
leave him like this.

39
00:04:06,333 --> 00:04:07,583
He's a wreck.

40
00:04:07,666 --> 00:04:09,416
Just our luck.

41
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:11,166
[Ragnarok]
Screw you guys.

42
00:04:13,708 --> 00:04:14,958
[Ragnarok]
Damn you, little girl!

43
00:04:15,041 --> 00:04:16,666
You're tiny!

44
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,916
[Ragnarok]
What the hell did you do?!

45
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,041
Why am I so little now?

46
00:04:20,125 --> 00:04:21,250
[Crona muffled]
Hey, get off me...!

47
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:22,375
How should I know?!

48
00:04:22,458 --> 00:04:23,291
Let go of her!

49
00:04:23,375 --> 00:04:24,250
[Ragnarok]
You and Crona...?

50
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:25,000
Friends...?

51
00:04:25,083 --> 00:04:26,666
You gotta be kidding me!

52
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,916
Who'd wanna be friends with
a pathetic thing like him...?

53
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,166
He isn't even any fun.

54
00:04:31,250 --> 00:04:32,750
[Crona]
Quit it... get off!

55
00:04:32,833 --> 00:04:34,000
[Ragnarok]
Wait, I got it!

56
00:04:34,083 --> 00:04:35,875
You wanna keep him around
as a punching bag!

57
00:04:35,958 --> 00:04:38,958
Bullying him is an excellent
way to reduce stress.

58
00:04:39,041 --> 00:04:40,833
That's what you want him for!

59
00:04:40,916 --> 00:04:42,458
Get goin' ya little freak.

60
00:04:42,541 --> 00:04:43,666
[Ragnarok]
Well, too bad.

61
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,791
I'm the only one who
gets to beat up Crona.

62
00:04:45,875 --> 00:04:47,208
[Ragnarok] He's mine!
You can't have him.

63
00:04:47,291 --> 00:04:48,041
Please get offa me...

64
00:04:48,125 --> 00:04:50,083
I said, get off now!

65
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,875
[Ragnarok screams]

66
00:05:02,458 --> 00:05:03,833
[Ragnarok] How could you
punch me, Crona...?

67
00:05:03,916 --> 00:05:05,250
I don't believe it...

68
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:08,250
Do you know how it
feels to be hit by you?!

69
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:10,541
No. How could I?

70
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:11,916
[Ragnarok]
Well, I'll tell you...!

71
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,125
It's like when you
haven't crapped

72
00:05:13,208 --> 00:05:14,625
in three days and
three nights...

73
00:05:14,708 --> 00:05:16,958
and then you get a
toilet-water splash back bonus

74
00:05:17,041 --> 00:05:18,583
when you unload it all.

75
00:05:18,666 --> 00:05:21,750
[Crona] That's gross,
and I don't get the comparison.

76
00:05:21,833 --> 00:05:24,000
[Ragnarok] You think I'm gonna
let you talk to me like that?

77
00:05:24,083 --> 00:05:25,750
You guys go ahead without me...

78
00:05:25,833 --> 00:05:27,583
I can handle things back here.

79
00:05:27,666 --> 00:05:28,750
I can hold him off.

80
00:05:28,833 --> 00:05:30,083
I won't let him through.

81
00:05:30,166 --> 00:05:31,625
Here we go!

82
00:05:31,708 --> 00:05:32,458
--Whatcha got under there, huh?
--Hey pervert, let go of me!

83
00:05:32,541 --> 00:05:33,791
Nice dress, pansy.

84
00:05:33,875 --> 00:05:35,250
Don't try to fight back.
You're pathetic.

85
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:36,333
Oh...kay...

86
00:05:36,416 --> 00:05:37,500
Sure thing. We'll just
leave it to you.

87
00:05:41,041 --> 00:05:43,875
Get him off! Somebody help me!

88
00:05:45,083 --> 00:05:46,875
Try not to die.

89
00:05:50,625 --> 00:05:51,791
[Maka]
The Seal Shrine...

90
00:05:51,875 --> 00:05:54,125
The Immortal Man's Tricks?

91
00:05:57,625 --> 00:05:58,791
[Maka] I wonder if
the others caught up

92
00:05:58,875 --> 00:06:00,875
with the ones who
had the black blood.

93
00:06:00,958 --> 00:06:03,708
[Soul] Are your
wounds healing okay?

94
00:06:03,791 --> 00:06:06,250
Some black scabs have
stopped the bleeding.

95
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:07,291
I think they're from the

96
00:06:07,375 --> 00:06:08,708
black blood
that was inside me...

97
00:06:08,791 --> 00:06:10,916
